testsuite.name: application.QuitChatUseCaseTest

testcase.name: should not quit from active channel if a channel is given but does not exist()
should quit from given channel but not active if exists and user is in it but not to join another channel()
should quit from active channel and set the active connection to null()
should throw exception if user is not logged in()
should not quit from any channel if user is not in any channel()
should quit from given channel if exists and user is in it()
should not quit from active channel if a channel is given but user is not in it()
should quit from active channel if none is given()
